      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still doing this. the lab results came back today and it's just... it's over. three years of work, and it's all gone. i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this research, and now that it's failed, i'm just empty. i'm so incredibly tired of fighting. i just want everything to stop.",
