      "content": "the \"peace\" i'm talking about isn't just taking a week off or going on vacation. i mean real peace. i'm so tired of the noise in my head, the constant pressure, the feeling that i'm just a ghost walking through my own life. it feels like there's no way to actually escape the weight of it all while i'm still stuck in this world. it feels like the only way to actually find stillness is to just... stop existing entirely. does that even make sense?",
